Another thing I want to know is Kachin News [http://www.kachinnews.com/] and Shan Herald [http://www.english.panglong.org/index.php] can be considered as reliable sources in the article [[Kachin conflict]] because Kachin News don't have contact address and printed newspapers, and because of the objectives and activities of Shan Herald. [http://www.english.panglong.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=173&Itemid=293] [[User:Laurence Watcher|Laurence Watcher]] ([[User talk:Laurence Watcher|talk]]) 12:56, 20 April 2014 (UTC)

